ave within skills like fletching, recipes that only followers of Karana and Tunare can make the combines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I don't see where it's a problem and I don't see where there will be a big community out cry for balance in this. I bet 1 person will complain. But this is something that is not a controversial topic was other ones.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I've been playing for 7 years. When I started Tailoring could go to 130 or 140'ish (reinforced leather armor). Before about ?Kurnak? or Velious?, they changes this to 115 (I got using quivers). When I started, Smithing went only to 175?, I htink, making banded armor. There were not other recipes. This was changed to 115(?) when a later expansion came out.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I can't remember trivials on jewel craft because i couldn't enchant stuff so it was pointless to start jewel craft.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Point is this game has evolved a great deal since way back when it started. I think gnome aaxps are in line for future evolution.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
